    "reviews_new_tDwEeQ": {
      "type": "reviews-new",
      "blocks": {
        "review_Kpnxmy": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>I've had eczema on my hands for a long time, and it's been tough to put on my hockey gloves. These glove liners have improved my experience by reducing friction against my skin. At first, it felt a bit weird, but now I've gotten so used to them that I actually don’t want to play without them anymore. They're just more comfortable.</p>",
            "author": "Linnea Petterson Dove",
            "prof": "Hockey player, Frölunda HC",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/profile-1_1.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_nJzNcB": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>My son's hands were bright pink and raw with all of the skin peeling off from wearing work gloves. I researched the best solutions and Drye liners were considered the best. Within a few days of wearing the liners, his hands were drastically improved. Within two weeks, they are completely healed and back to normal. I cannot believe the difference! Worth every penny!</p>",
            "author": "Debby Fields",
            "prof": "Unknown",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/360_F_1029660575_DPdwknEa7hiEveRujsBmxXLfFxJM31UA.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_PBtAQE": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>I used to have issues with cracked hands and eczema, These gloves have helped a lot. No more itching or sweating, and they fit well.</p>",
            "author": "Adam Hemberg",
            "prof": "Electrical Mechanic, Tesla",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/DRYE_Moisture_Wicking_Gloves.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_cEy6bX": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>I have eczema and these gloves have been the best things I bought for my hands. I have to wear latex gloves all day for work. I wear the DRYE gloves then the latex gloves on top. Every hour, I would change my gloves and notice the sweat on my DRYE - but my hands remain dried. When my skin is dried and cracked, I would wear just the DRYE at home and my hands feel better. Thank you so much for making these! </p>",
            "author": "Phuong Ngo",
            "prof": "Unknown",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/360_F_1029660575_DPdwknEa7hiEveRujsBmxXLfFxJM31UA.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_hxztzQ": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Incredibly good gloves for someone with dry skin. Big plus that these can handle industrial washing and still work perfectly afterward.</p>",
            "author": "Jens Stålnacke",
            "prof": "Mining worker",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/profile-2_1_af5523d5-253b-4d76-86ec-31ea3176efdf.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_UhWpVj": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>They keep my hands dry and comfortable. It took a little getting used to, but now they’re just part of my routine.</p>",
            "author": "Emilia A",
            "prof": "Pastry Chef, Robin Delselius Bageri",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Biodegradable_Moisture-Wicking_Gloves_for_Eczema-modified.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_H4BCLE": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>They’re comfortable to wear, and my hands feel less dry and irritated now. Definitely an improvement.</p>",
            "author": "Sofia Malmberg",
            "prof": "Hairdresser, Nikita Hair",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Capture_b4ce3c76-09e5-464d-a280-951cb732a1c1-modified.webp"
          }
        },
        "review_3iiLTh": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Thank you! I have hand eczema, and these gloves have helped me a lot in my daily life.</p>",
            "author": "Linn Bäckström",
            "prof": "Pastry chef",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/profile-3_1_42cb4e30-4112-4c63-88fc-ab9d3d2cff68.webp"
          }
        }
      },
